# sonnet-antipatterns-top — Sonnet with anti-patterns moved to Step 0 of triage.md.
# The overlay triage.md lives at test-lab/overlays/antipatterns-top/triage.md.
# run-test.sh copies this over .claude/commands/triage.md for the run's duration,
# then restores.
CONFIG_NAME=sonnet-antipatterns-top
CLAUDE_MODEL=sonnet
TRIAGE_MD_OVERLAY=test-lab/overlays/antipatterns-top/triage.md
